Redeclaration              	âœ… Allowed	              âŒ Not allowed	      âŒ Not allowed
Reassignment	              âœ… Allowed  	            âœ… Allowed	          âŒ Not allowed
Hoisting	                  Hoisted â†’ undefined	      Hoisted â†’ TDZ	        Hoisted â†’ TDZ
Initialization	            Optional	                Optional	            Mandatory at declaration


